data.description: Better than new 3 bedroom plus office that could be used as bedroom/2.5 baths Murphy Kaufman Fall 2016 Model Home ready for new owners as Seller got transferred.  Luxury vinyl plank floors in main areas, large tile in baths, carpet in BRs. Beautiful kitchen w/ black stainless Samsung appliances, white subway backsplash, 12' island w/ lots of storage & terra stone counters. Split plan w/ pocket door to close off guest rooms.  Large master suite w/ walk in closet, garden tub & shower.  Multi sliders open completely to tiled patio w/ electric & ceiling fan/light.  6' vinyl privacy fence w/ 4' and 12' gates.  Tankless water heater, Taexx tubes for pest control and termite bond. All cabinet drawers are equipped with soft close feature. Extras listed on attached document!
